                text-shadow:0 0 8px rgba(255,90,44,0.7)">Tommy's</div>
    <div style="font-family:var(--f-pixel);font-size:22px;letter-spacing:6px;color:var(--neon-blue);
                text-shadow:0 0 8px rgba(43,184,255,0.7)">CLUB</div>
</div>

<div class="wf-eyebrow mb-3" style="color:var(--neon-cyan)">Exclusive &middot; Anonymous &middot; Invite-Only</div>

<div class="about-prose">
    <p class="lead">Club9 is a private space for a carefully chosen circle — a place to write freely, think openly, and connect without the noise of the public internet.</p>

    <p>Membership is limited by design. This isn't a platform built for scale — it's built for depth. Every voice here was let in intentionally, and that makes all the difference.</p>

    <p>Anonymity is a first-class feature. You choose your alias, your avatar, your presence. What matters is what you write, not who the world thinks you are.</p>

    <h2>What happens here</h2>
</div>

